MasterChef Ireland - Series 3, Episode 12




The seven hopefuls vie for a place in the quarter-final. They are given a pasta machine and an open pantry of ingredients then asked to create something that inspires passion and shows the simplicity and versatility of a fine-dining dish. The cooks have 90 minutes to complete the task, at the end of which one of them will be going home.




Original Air Date: 09-Apr-2014
